{
  "stem": "3690.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, yeah, we heard that, but I think he got taken to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, [SOBBING] and we-- we-- we couldn't-- in the beginning, I just couldn't-- no way to get organized to get to Sweden.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my-- they said, my-- your father is in Theresienstadt, in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Theresienstadt was Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I could go there with no problem.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just me, myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother was kind of afraid to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I says, if you don't want to go, I'll go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, and then, before they-- all that happen, we finally talked in the authorities that they let us back in our own home, where we used to live.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew this, our mother and father buried stuff underground in one of the rooms.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So all of us Jewish boys went there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got shovels from the neighbors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the son-of-a-guns, these neighbors, squealed on us to the-- to the authorities, as we digging up [BACKGROUND NOISE] American money, the gold and silver and valuables.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we got out something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We tried to get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And sure enough, as much as we get out, it wasn't much, but it was more than nothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, it was worth a nice, few hundred dollars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next morning, early in the morning, about 5 o'clock in the morning, they knock on the door.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were Russian Banderovcis, Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we slept all in one room, on the floors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a big carpet, a huge carpet, you know, like a throw rug.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and the Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, you Jews, you dug up a lot of valuables and gold and silver and who knows what else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- we want those valuables.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
